    "Sentiment analysis of public discussions highlights this complex emotional landscape, where excitement and fear coexist.",
    "The adoption of generative AI is reshaping economies and cultures worldwide.",
    "Economically, it is automating repetitive tasks, boosting productivity, and even creating new job categories.",
    "However, it also threatens to displace workers, particularly in roles involving routine cognitive tasks.",
    "The cultural impact varies significantly by region."
